  <brief_title>Efficacy of Proton Pump Inhibitors in Gastrointestinal Erosions and/or Ulcers</brief_title>
  <official_title>RCT Using Bonopurazan or Esomeprazole in Patients With NSAIDs-induced Erosions and/or Ulcers</official_title>
