  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to collect the data of clinical efficacy and safety after the usage
      of bonoprazon and esomeprazole when the patients take NSAIDs more than 2 weeks and have
      gastrointestinal symptoms who have had gastrointestinal erosions and/or ulcers in the past.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
